Class UserEvent.AnEvent

java.lang.Object
  models.UserEvent.AnEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
UserEvent.ListenTo, UserEvent.UserLogon
Enclosing class:
UserEvent
public abstract static class UserEvent.AnEvent
extends java.lang.Object

UserEvents are dropped into the User.userEvents queue, which is listened to by chat clients for notifications, including friends signing on or leaving, or new chat rooms to listen to. These events will also be served serialized into JSON objects. They are immediately pushed into the User.userEvents stream when they are created.
